g.title: j3344135747
g.text: How in the ever-loving bloody hell did you convince *Quincy* of all people to speak to me on your behalf?

g.title: j949808710
g.text: I just needed to apologize to you, and didn't know how else to do it.

g.title: j4024417561
g.text: I have no clue what you're talking about. [End.]

g.title: j810087369
g.text: I... just didn't know how else to tell you I had feelings for you.

g.title: j2037038947
g.text: Points for the surprise factor, I suppose. I certainly wasn't expecting that. And... very well. Apology accepted.

g.title: j963591469
g.text: I do have to admit you've been on my mind a great deal lately.

g.title: j3629503963
g.text: You did have a shot with me, and you chose to walk away. But... Quincy was convincing. If you'd like to give this another go, I'm willing to give it a try.

g.title: j702025363
g.text: How about walking up to me in the Hub, and simply saying, 'mate, I have feelings for you?' Did that ever cross your mind?

g.title: j2812790530
g.text: If you'd like to give this a go, I'm willing to give it a try.

g.title: j317645313
g.text: ...Has anyone ever told you, you are *proper* nuts?

g.title: j3879737818
g.text: Sometimes I simply do not know what to do with you.

g.title: j3860522506
g.text: Well. Glad to have all that sorted then. Shall we?

g.title: j1492481394
g.text: Well. No point in fussing about it now. I... have to admit you've been on my mind. If you'd like to give this a go, I'm willing to give it a try.
